 the ejecta show only small deviations\nfrom spherical symmetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Dec 2009 01:35:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2010 16:43:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
